\int\frac{x^2}{(x^2+4)^2}dx=\int x\frac{x}{(x^2+4)^2}dx=\frac{1}{2} \int x(\frac{-1}{x^2+4})'dx=\frac{1}{2}(\frac{-x}{x^2+4} +\int \frac{1}{x^2+4}dx)=\frac{1}{2}(\frac{-x}{x^2+4} +\frac{1}{2}\arctan\frac{x}{2}) +C
